     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Dark theme. Defines all Dock* and Panel_*
         resource keys used by the shared Dark/ control templates and PanelCommon.xaml.
         Also defines TabColorizer styles specific to the dark tab strip.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed by DarkTheme.xaml as the first merged dictionary.
         Shared by DarkTheme; VS2022DarkTheme and VisualStudioTheme use their own
         Colors.xaml files for theme-specific palette variations.
     ========================================================== -->

